               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960622-52-cd293" type="crimeDate">11th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960622-52-off292 t17960622-52-cd293"></join>, six silver desert spoons, value 30s. and six tea spoons, value 18s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17960622-52-victim562" type="victimName">
